just_use dm.go

# label: WORKHORSE
# role: supports feature — 1:1 direct message CRUD
#   (get-or-create conversation, list convs, send message, list messages)

Minor domain invariant worth noting: a conversation pair is stored as
(min_id, max_id) in dm_conversations. `getOrCreateConversation` sorts
lo/hi before insert, so the pair is canonical regardless of who
initiated. Lookups must preserve that ordering or they'll miss.
